ired Twitter and named himself =E2=80=98chief twit,=E2=80=99 a role analogo=
us to CEO. Musk also testified that he asked approximately 50 Tesla enginee=
rs to =E2=80=98volunteer=E2=80=99 to help him evaluate Twitter=E2=80=99s en=
gineering team. No one on the [Tesla] Board called Musk to tell him not to =
do this. In the weeks prior to trial, Musk spent the =E2=80=98lion=E2=80=99=
s share=E2=80=99 of his time at Twitter.=E2=80=9D


