<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I do see Elon Musk=E2=80=99s point. He runs, w=
hat, six companies? SpaceX, Neuralink, Twitter/X, the tunnel one, xAI, prob=
ably some I=E2=80=99m forgetting. And Tesla Inc., the only one of them that=
 is public, though for a while he also had SolarCity Corp. before (controve=
rsially) <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34187745.=
258395/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDQt=
