2" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">  merging it into Tesla</a>. Each of these companies does some=
thing different=E2=80=94=C2=A0rocket science, brain surgery, posting on the=
 internet, tunnels, artificial intelligence, cars =E2=80=94=C2=A0but there =
is overlap.=C2=A0They seem to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusines=
s.com/click/34187745.258395/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYnVzaW5lc3NpbnNpZGVyLmNvbS9lbG9=
uLW11c2stYXV0aG9yaXplcy10ZXNsYS1zcGFjZXgtYm9yaW5nLWV4ZWN1dGl2ZXMtd29yay10d2=
l0dGVyLXJlcG9ydC0yMDIyLTEy/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBf248ba50" itemprop=3D"S=
toryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> shar=
e employees</a> and a certain ambitious science fiction ethos, and you coul=
d imagine futuristic projects that could be done at any of them.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At all but one of his companies, he could stro=
ll into the boardroom, throw a big=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/34187745.258395/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vc=
