vdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDEzMSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg=
/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB33495d67" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"ite=
mscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !i=
mportant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bo=
ttom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">bag of ketamine</a> down onto t=
he table, and say =E2=80=9CI need the company to spend $50 million to build=
 a giant golden statue of me riding a rocket,=E2=80=9D<a class=3D"footnote-=
index" href=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none =
!important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-=
bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; di=
splay: inline-block;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a>=C2=A0and</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">the board would be like =E2=80=9Cyes =
definitely let=E2=80=99s do it,=E2=80=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom:=
 5px;">the board members themselves probably are, or represent, big shareho=
lders of the company, and as shareholders they would happily go along with =
the statue plan to keep Musk happy and dedicated to their company,</li>=09<=
li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">the=C2=A0<em>other=C2=A0</em>shareholders,=
 the ones without board seats, are probably even bigger <a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34187745.258395/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb=
21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMTAtMDMvZXZlcnlvbmUtd2FudGVkLXRv=
LWJ1eS10d2l0dGVyLXdpdGgtZWxvbj9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMTMxMjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWV=
kaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDAxMzEmdXRtX2NhbX=
BhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB55f9c0d1" itemprop=3D"StoryL=
ink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; tex=
t-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-colo=
r: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  Musk fan=
s</a>, and are probably working on their own Musk statues in their garages =
anyway, so they=E2=80=99ll be fine with the company spending their money on=
 a corporate gold statue, and</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">nobo=
dy else really has any standing to complain.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And so in fact when Musk went to SpaceX and <a=
 href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34187745.258395/aHR0=
cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDktMDYvc3BhY2V=
4LWxvYW5lZC1lbG9uLW11c2stc29tZS1tb25leT9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMTMxMjRfTU9ORVlTVFVGRi=
Z1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yNDAxMzEmd=
XRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBc94b3888" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
  asked to borrow $1 billion until payday</a> so that he could buy Twitter =
Inc., the board was like =E2=80=9Chere=E2=80=99s the check, we=E2=80=99ve l=
eft the amount blank, take whatever you need.=E2=80=9D And, look, was there=
 a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34187745.258395=
/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9idXNpbmVzcy9lbG9uLW11c2stc3BhY2V4LWxvYW4tMjY5YT=
IxNjg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB54249f93" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Wall Street Journal art=
icle</a> saying =E2=80=9Chey that=E2=80=99s weird=E2=80=9D? There was; it w=
as weird. Did anything come of that? No. SpaceX could just do that: Musk co=
ntrols SpaceX, the board loves him, the shareholders love him, nobody in a =
position to complain has any complaints, and everybody else is in no positi=
on to complain.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is all at least arguably rational. The an=
alysis is something like:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Elon Musk is an unusual cat, in some =
ways that make him really good at building valuable and innovative companie=
s, and in some ways that make him difficult and destructive,=C2=A0and also =
in some random ways that are just weird. You can=E2=80=99t get <em>just=C2=
=A0</em>Good Elon; you take the good with the bad with the random.=C2=A0</l=
i>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">He spends all of his time at work, a=
pparently, at his various companies. But he probably does neglect some of t=
he companies, at times, for the other ones. There are only 168 hours in the=
 week and he=E2=80=99s doing a lot of full-time jobs. And there=C2=A0<em>ar=
e=C2=A0</em>projects that you could imagine him doing at any of his compani=
es.=C2=A0At least <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/=
34187745.258395/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQ=
tMDEtMTUvZWxvbi1tdXNrLXdhbnRzLWdyZWF0ZXItY29udHJvbC1vZi10ZXNsYS1iZWZvcmUtYn=
VpbGRpbmctaXRzLWFpP2NtcGlkPUJCRDAxMzEyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1ha=
WwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDEzMSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9u=
ZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0d0dd758" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemsc=
ope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoratio=
n: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000;=
 border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Tesla</a>, xAI and <=
a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34187745.258395/aHR=
0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL25ld3NsZXR0ZXJzLzIwMjMtMTItMTQvZWxvbi=
1tdXNrLXMtZ3Jvay1yZXByZXNlbnRzLWEtc2VyaW91cy10aHJlYXQtdG8tY2hhdGdwdD9jbXBpZ=
