al intelligence models, for instance.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5p=
x;">His efforts appear to be=C2=A0<em>extremely=C2=A0</em>valuable to those=
 companies, creating surely hundreds of billions of dollars of=C2=A0 value =
for their shareholders.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-2" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; =
background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[2]</span>
</a>
</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">If he wants some weird thing =E2=
=80=94=C2=A0a hypothetical gold statue, a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/34187745.258395/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9=
