<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Why did Tesla have to =E2=80=9Cgive=E2=80=9D a=
nything in these circumstances? Musk owned 21.9% of Tesla at the time of th=
e Grant. If the goals were retention, engagement, and alignment, then Musk=
