throughout this litigation that he was a lifer who intended to stay at Tesl=
a for the remainder of his days (or until he becomes =E2=80=9Ctoo crazy=E2=
=80=9D), with or without the Grant.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The principal defect with Defendants=E2=80=99 =
give/get argument (indeed, their fair price argument as a whole) is that it=
