our shareholders, but you also have=C2=A0<em>genuinely outside shareholders=
</em>, index funds and activists and gadflies and anyone else who wants to =
buy stock.=C2=A0If you run a private company, even one incorporated in Dela=
ware (as, for instance, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/=
