<span>[15]</span>
</a>=C2=A0There is some overlap among Musk=E2=80=99s companies; some part o=
f the value of each of them comes from the fact that Elon Musk gets surpris=
ing profitable ideas sometimes, and he might implement them at <em>that=C2=
=A0</em>company. So the threat is real. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
